the police are still investigating the fire accident.
</P>
<P>
In November last year, as many as 1.250 shops in a five-storey
shopping center in the city burned down, causing about 304.4
million US dollars of material losses.
</P>
<P>
Fire fighters tried to control the blaze for 84 hours, making
the incident the biggest inferno in Jakarta.  
