(INA) reported. In a televised address today marking the 6th
anniversary of the start of the Gulf War in 1991, the president
said Iraq's enemies destroyed the weapons and supplies of the
Iraqi army and the country's national industry, but the Iraqis
were not defeated, according to the INA.
