arrangements for joint-venture programs involving the government,
the donor community, the private sector and non-government
organizations.
</P>
<P>
The UNDP is a UN program committed to supporting countries to
achieve sustainable development through assistance in building the
capacity to design and carry out development projects.
</P>
<P>
The program includes poverty eradication, employment creation,
sustainable livelihoods, the empowerment of women and the
protection and regeneration of the environment.  
