Samant. Most shops and business establishments in the city and
suburbs remained closed.
</P>
<P>
According to Joint Commissioner of Police R.S. Sharma, security
has been beefed up in sensitive areas and all check posts in the
city against any untoward incident.
</P>
<P>
The motive of killing Samant is yet to be known and the
assassins are still at large.  
