<HEADLINE> Argentina, Uruguay Enter Semifinals of Beach Soccer </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
RIO DE JANEIRO, January 16 (Xinhua) -- Both Argentina and
Uruguay recorded their respective wins on Thursday, entering the
semifinals of the third annual Beach Soccer World Championships.
</P>
<P>
Argentina defeated France 3-1 and Uruguay defeated Italy 7-6,
attaining the last two spots for the last four.
</P>
<P>
Both Brazil and the United States obtained their semifinal
tickets on Wednesday as Brazil won 10-2 against Portugal and the
United States defeated Japan 2-1.
</P>
<P>
In the other match on Thursday, Brazil beat the United States
5-3, which had no bearing for the semifinals. 
</P>
</TEXT>
